\ul DAY 3 \ulnone : RAMESHWARAM - TIRUCHENDUR - KANYAKUMARI\
Early morning take Shpatik linga Darshan at the famous Ramanathan temple - a Master Piece in Dravidian Architecture. Proceed to Kanyakumari via Tiruchendur \'96 the sea shore temple of Subrahmanyam, is one of the delightful spots sanctified and venerated by every Hindu. Arrive in Kanyakumari. Enjoy sunset in the evening.
\f0\b Extra Topping :\'a0
\f1\b0 Coconut water at Rameshwaram\
\
\ul DAY 4 \ulnone : KANYAKUMARI - TRIVENDRUM\
Visit Swami Vivekanand Rock Memorial. Visit the meditation hall and the smarak. Visit Kanyakumari mandir (One of the Fifty Two Shakti Peethas), Tri smudra milan & Gandhi mandapam. Evening visit Suchindram temple. (One of the Fifty Two Shakti Peethas). Proceed to Trivendrum. Arrive in Trivendrum.
\f0\b Extra Topping :\'a0
\f1\b0 Targola / Coconut water at Gandhi Mandapam\
\
\ul DAY 5 \ulnone : DEPARTURE FROM TRIVENDRUM\
In the morning Visit Padmanabh Swami Temple, Raja Ravi Varma Art Gallery and Napier Museum (subject to operation). Proceed to Trivendrum Airport. Board the flight to your Home Town. Tour Conclude\
